window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I had my whole life planned out... until I met a hockey player obsessed with breaking all of my rules.</b></p> <p>My five simple rules for hooking up keep me from being distracted. Now that I'm so close to landing my dream internship, nothing is going to make me break them. Not even a protective hockey player with clear grey eyes, a sharp jaw, and a body that makes my breath catch.</p> <p>Until Jax wins a bet and one kiss has me breaking them all.</p> <p><i>Rule Number Five</i> is book one in the Rule Breaker series from <i>USA Today </i>bestselling author J. Wilder. If you want squishy, warm, happy feelings, and quality spice her books are for you.</p>"; 
